// ** Routes Imports
import AppRoutes from './Apps'
import FormRoutes from './Forms'
import PagesRoutes from './Pages'
import TablesRoutes from './Tables'
import ChartMapsRoutes from './ChartsMaps'
import DashboardRoutes from './Dashboards'
import UiElementRoutes from './UiElements'
import MasterMeetingsRoutes from './Mom'
import PageLayoutsRoutes from './PageLayouts'
import HrRoutes from './Hr'
import EcrRoutes from './Ecr'
import BusinessRoutes from './BusinessTrip'
import PurchaseRoutes from './Purchase'

// ** Document title
const TemplateTitle = '%s -Star Admin Panel'

// ** Default Route
const DefaultRoute = '/master/user'

// ** Merge Routes
const Routes = [
  ...DashboardRoutes,
  ...AppRoutes,
  ...PagesRoutes,
  ...UiElementRoutes,
  ...MasterMeetingsRoutes,
  ...PageLayoutsRoutes,
  ...FormRoutes,
  ...TablesRoutes,
  ...ChartMapsRoutes,
  ...HrRoutes,
  ...EcrRoutes,
  ...BusinessRoutes,
  ...PurchaseRoutes
]


export { DefaultRoute, TemplateTitle, Routes }
export default { DefaultRoute, TemplateTitle, Routes }
